Package farm

Interface Upgradeable

All Known Implementing Classes:
DistinguishedFarmer, Farmer, LegendaryFarmer, RegisteredFarmer
public interface Upgradeable
This interface provides the contracts for creating an upgradeable class.

  • Method Details

    • upgrade

      Player upgrade()
      This method checks if the player is eligible to upgrade into the next farmer type and upgrades if the requirements are met.

      If the player is eligible, a new instance of the upgraded player is made.

      Returns:
      a new instance of the current object but as its subclass.
